participant_id.Description: Unique BIDS identifier for the participant in this study.

subjectkey.Description: The NDAR Global Unique Identifier (GUID) for research subject

src_subject_id.Description: Subject ID how it's defined in lab/project

interview_age.Description: Age in months at the time of the interview/test/sampling/imaging. | Age is rounded to chronological month. If the research participant is 15-days-old at time of interview, the appropriate value would be 0 months. If the participant is 16-days-old, the value would be 1 month.

interview_date.Description: Date on which the interview/genetic test/sampling/imaging/biospecimen was completed. MM/DD/YYYY

sex.Description: Sex of subject at birth | M = Male; F = Female; O=Other; NR = Not reported

eventname.Description: The event name for which the data was collected

strp_scr_script_elapsedtime.Description: Time it took to run script (in ms)

strp_scr_comp_platform.Description: The platform the script was run on

strp_scr_values_completed.Description: 0 = script was not completed (prematurely aborted); 1 = script was completed (all conditions run)

strp_scr_val_acc_prac1.Description: Proportion correct in final practice1 run

strp_scr_val_acc_prac2.Description: Proportion correct in final practice2 run

strp_scr_acc_all.Description: Proportion correct overall (across all test trials)

strp_scr_acc_morecongr.Description: Proportion correct in "more congruent pairings" block

strp_scr_acc_morecongrcongr.Description: Proportion correct on congruent trials in "more congruent pairings" block

strp_scr_acc_morecongrincongr.Description: Proportion correct on incongruent trials in "more congruent pairings" block

strp_scr_acc_equal.Description: Proportion correct in "equal numbers of congruent/incongruent pairings" block

strp_scr_acc_equalcongr.Description: Proportion correct in "equal numbers of congruent/incongruent pairings" block

strp_scr_acc_equalincongr.Description: Proportion correct in "equal numbers of congruent/incongruent pairings" block

strp_scr_acc_congr.Description: Proportion correct in "congruent" pairings trials (across test blocks)

strp_scr_acc_incongr.Description: Proportion correct in "incongruent" pairings trials (across test blocks)

strp_scr_mnrt_morecongr.Description: Mean correct latency (in ms) in "more congruent pairings" block

strp_scr_mnrt_morecongrcongr.Description: Mean correct latency (in ms) on congruent trials in "more congruent pairings" block

strp_scr_mnrt_morecongrincongr.Description: Mean correct latency (in ms) on incongruent trials in "more congruent pairings" block

strp_scr_mnrt_eq.Description: Mean correct latency (in ms) in "equal numbers of congruent/incongruent pairings" block

strp_scr_mnrt_eqcongr.Description: Mean correct latency (in ms) in "equal numbers of congruent/incongruent

strp_scr_mnrt_eqincongr.Description: Mean correct latency (in ms) in "equal numbers of congruent/incongruent pairings" block

strp_scr_mnrt_congr.Description: mean correct latency (in ms) in "congruent" pairings trials (across test blocks)

strp_scr_mnrt_incongr.Description: Mean correct latency (in ms) in "incongruent" pairings trials (across test blocks)
